    detailed_description:
      '<h2 class="bb_tag"><strong>Aimlabs is the #1 aim trainer, trusted by over 40 million players! Are you ready to upgrade your aiming skills?</strong></h2><p class="bb_paragraph">Aimlabs is a training platform to help sharpen up your core FPS aiming skills. Aimlabs offers a comprehensive set of tools to improve your aim, regardless of which FPS you play. It provides curated training scenarios that will turn you into an aim God in no time.</p><p class="bb_paragraph">Dive into specifically designed training exercises to master the art of flicking, tracking and switching. Aimlabs’ detailed analysis feedback gives you valuable insights and guides you towards rapid improvement.</p><p class="bb_paragraph">Aimlabs is continuously updated with new features to ensure compatibility with a wide range of games. Whether you\'re a beginner or a seasoned pro, Aimlabs will help to give you a competitive edge.</p><p class="bb_paragraph"></p><p class="bb_paragraph"><div class="bb_img_ctn"><video class="bb_img" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/714010/extras/16a9df8737ee67a9cfeefb3edb61d761.poster.avif?t=1748985307" ><source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/714010/extras/16a9df8737ee67a9cfeefb3edb61d761.webm?t=1748985307" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"><source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/714010/extras/16a9df8737ee67a9cfeefb3edb61d761.mp4?t=1748985307" type="video/mp4"></video></div></p><h2 class="bb_tag"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class="bb_paragraph"></p><ul class="bb_ul"><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Aim Training</strong>: Master aim fundamentals with tasks that train flicking, tracking, and switching!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Game Specific Training</strong>: Find the best training playlists tailored for your FPS game of choice!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Universal Sensitivity Finder:</strong> Find your optimal sensitivity, for any game!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Valorant Training Center</strong>: Train fundamental VALORANT mechanics like crosshair placement on 1:1 map recreations!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Adaptive Tasks</strong>: Play every task at your optimal difficulty level to personalize your aim training!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Aimlabs Academy</strong>: Learn how to apply your training to your favorite FPS games with step-by-step masterclasses hand-crafted by the experts. New lessons drop every month!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Discovery AI Coach</strong>: Get aim advice from your own personal AI aim coach!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Aim Analysis</strong>: Reveal your aim strengths + weaknesses with detailed performance feedback!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Sensitivity Matcher</strong>: Aim train on the exact same sensitivity you use in your FPS games!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Ranked Seasons</strong>: Benchmark your aim and earn your Aimlabs Rank to see how you compare against other aimers!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Leaderboards</strong>: Compete against others and show off how good your aim is!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Player Customization</strong>: Customize your aim training with weapon skins, avatars, banners, titles, and more!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Battlepass</strong>: Earn exclusive rewards by playing Aimlabs every season!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Replays</strong>: Watch and learn from how others aim with replays of every task played!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Playlist Of The Day</strong>: Earn Aim Credits while you train to redeem for awesome rewards, everyday!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Customizable Environments</strong>: Take complete control of your training environment!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Mouse + Controller support</strong>: Train your way, regardless of your input device!</p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Player Streaks</strong>: Track your training progress by playing every day! </p></li><li><p class="bb_paragraph"><strong>Continuous Updates</strong>: New features will be added as we create innovative ways to improve your aim. We’re always adding fresh tasks and content to ensure compatibility with a wide range of games.</p></li></ul><h2 class="bb_tag"><strong>What players are saying:</strong></h2><h2 class="bb_tag">“Aim Lab made me not suck at Valorant.”</h2><p class="bb_paragraph"> - <strong>Someone in Discord</strong> </p><h2 class="bb_tag">“I just love playing Aim Lab. My Wingman shots have definitely improved.&quot;</h2><p class="bb_paragraph"> - <strong> Lululuvely</strong> </p><h2 class="bb_tag">“Aim Lab removed my left-side weakness”</h2><p class="bb_paragraph"> - <strong>King George</strong> </p><h2 class="bb_tag">“Why go to the gym when you have Aim Lab?” </h2><p class="bb_paragraph"> - <strong>Aceu</strong>  </p><h2 class="bb_tag">“Aim Lab made me get a girlfriend&quot;</h2><p class="bb_paragraph"> - <strong>Someone on Twitter</strong></p>',
